snippet.title: [Smash Bros. Wii U/3DS] Peach's Castle (64) Gameplay
snippet.description: Four Super Mario characters fight for fun on the Peach's Castle stage,  which is part of the new Super Smash Bros. Wii U/3DS DLC!
